  "title": "Technician",
  "description": "<p>Job Scope</p><ul><li>To carry out routine scheduled Preventive Maintenance (PM) on semiconductor process equipment;</li><li>To work in a cleanroom environment and strictly follow equipment maintenance procedures and methods;</li><li>To install new process kits and ensure that equipment is working correctly by carrying out quality inspections on PM jobs;</li><li>To liaise with client’s engineering departments to ensure proper handover of equipment after PM;</li><li>To keep proper record of PM tasks completed, maintain 5S in the working environment and upkeep of maintenance tools.</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Able to converse in English;</li><li>Physically fit, energetic and agile;</li><li>Must be committed with positive attitude;</li><li>Prior experience working in a semiconductor industry is a plus.</li></ul><p><br /></p>",
